text: Insaniyat (, ) is a Pakistani Urdu black and white movie. It was produced by A. Hameed. This movie is one of the masterpieces of the director Shabab Kiranvi. The movie starred Waheed Murad, Zeba, Tariq Aziz, Firdous and Nanna. This movie is one of the hit movies of Waheed Murad.
